{"tid":651902,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Nikola 告 Tesla 侵犯其電動卡車專利求償20億美元","createTime":"2018-05-03T12:31:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-03T13:27:45.000Z","uid":36964,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"15172261992a7023f22df91835d0158f18ce517c","tid":651902,"uid":36964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T12:31:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.reuters.com/article/us-tesla-lawsuit-nikola-motor/nikola-motor-sues-tesla-alleging-design-patent-violation-idUSKBN1I30DN\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Farticle%2Fus-tesla-lawsuit-nikola-motor%2Fnikola-motor-sues-tesla-alleging-design-patent-violation-idUSKBN1I30DN&d=9taV22dOq6wRUAuP5TGQxUbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=3d85ba4a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Farticle%2Fus-tesla-lawsuit-nikola-motor%2Fnikola-motor-sues-tesla-alleging-design-patent-violation-idUSKBN1I30DN&h=3bdad53e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.reuters.com/article/us-tesla-lawsuit-nikola-motor/nikola-motor-sues-tesla-alleging-design-patent-violation-idUSKBN1I30DN</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20180502/bkn-20180502205054242-0502_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20180502%2Fbkn-20180502205054242-0502_00842_001.html&d=9taV22dOq6wRUAuP5TGQxUbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=f2ace970\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20180502/bkn-20180502205054242-0502_00842_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n外媒報道，特斯拉(Tesla)被研發電氫卡車的初創公司Nikola Motor Co.控告侵犯專利，追索20億美元(約156億港元)。<br />\n<br />\nNikola於5月1日提出的訴訟指出，特斯拉複製其於2016年5月推出的半掛式卡車(Semi Truck)設計。<br />\n<br />\n據法院文件，Nikola於2017年11月初向特斯拉發信，指出特斯拉的電動半掛式卡車(Tesla Semi)特徵與其產品相似，包括環繞式擋風玻璃、由中間開啟的車門、以及空氣動力學機身。Nikola要求特斯拉於侵權問題解決後，才公開發表Tesla Semi。惟文件顯示，特斯拉未有回應，更於2017年11月16日公布該款車型。<br />\n<br />\nNikola表示，特斯拉推出Tesla Semi引起市場混淆，對Nikola吸引投資者和合作夥伴造成負面影響，所以向特斯拉追討超過20億美元的賠償，大約等於特斯拉公布Tesla Semi後增加的市值。特斯拉發言人周二(5月1日)表示：「這場訴訟明顯沒有任何價值。」<br />\n<br />\n特斯拉的Tesla Semi於今年3月首次展示貨物載運，但預期於2019年前都不會進行量產，而首批交車時間定於2020年。不少大型公司，如UPS、百事可樂、沃爾瑪(Walmart)等都已預購。<br />\n<br />\nNikola於今年1月宣布，計劃於在亞利桑那州建立一個價值10億美元的工廠。當時它聲稱已接下超過8,000張氫燃料電池電動半掛式卡車的預購單，並預計於2021年開始生產。<br />\n<br />\nNikola和特斯拉之前也曾發生爭執，有趣的是，兩家公司的名字都是源於同一個發明家－Nikola Tesla.<br />\n<br />\n特斯拉將於周三(5月2日)美股收市後公布第1季業績。<br />\n<br />\nNikola Tesla <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98f91a248b9e5b30ba00d9d8fc5146ded101f626","tid":651902,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T12:47:51.000Z","msg":"又真係抄足"},{"pid":"1bd19fb7f2809f6ca5a3072fa60b512166af1642","tid":651902,"uid":36964,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T12:49:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.teslarati.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/tesla-semi-vs-nikola-one-e1522999098959.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.teslarati.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F10%2Ftesla-semi-vs-nikola-one-e1522999098959.jpg&h=699e61d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://a57.foxnews.com/images.foxnews.com/content/fox-news/auto/2018/05/02/tesla-accused-copycat-semi-truck-design-in-2-billion-patent-lawsuit/_jcr_content/par/featured_image/media-0.img.jpg/931/524/1525274621611.jpg?ve=1&amp;tl=1&amp;text=big-top-image\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fa57.foxnews.com%2Fimages.foxnews.com%2Fcontent%2Ffox-news%2Fauto%2F2018%2F05%2F02%2Ftesla-accused-copycat-semi-truck-design-in-2-billion-patent-lawsuit%2F_jcr_content%2Fpar%2Ffeatured_image%2Fmedia-0.img.jpg%2F931%2F524%2F1525274621611.jpg%3Fve%3D1%26tl%3D1%26text%3Dbig-top-image&h=4b82c663&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e384ba683bd544edce38874fb5ce62c4440a2848","tid":651902,"uid":29606,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTim